                    'UPGRADE_WARNING: Couldn't resolve default property of object rsCustOrdDtl.GetValue(Balance_Qty). Click for more: 'ms-help://MS.VSCC.v80/dv_commoner/local/redirect.htm?keyword="6A50421D-15FE-4896-8A1B-2EC21E9037B2"'
